          <title>Rich Rodriguez is returning to West Virginia for a second stint as head coach</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Rich Rodriguez is returning to West Virginia for a second stint as head coach at his alma mater. Athletic director Wren Baker announced the hiring on Thursday, 17 years after Rodriguez made a hasty exit for what became a disastrous three-year experiment at Michigan.]]></description>
