          <title>Dosunmu's first career triple-double leads Bulls 139-124 over Spurs</title>
          <description><![CDATA[SAN ANTONIO (AP) — Nikola Vucevic had a season-high 39 points, Ayo Dosunmu had 27 points, 11 assists and 10 rebounds and the Chicago Bulls beat the San Antonio Spurs 139-124 on Thursday night with Victor Wembanyama sidelined with a back injury.]]></description>
